{"tid":196533,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【老漢推車落湖】男友酒後駕駛，意外後不顧而去被拘！","createTime":"2017-04-11T11:24:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-11T11:24:56.000Z","uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"efb5593d51bc4a6ab4952a83f3593e53b808c971","tid":196533,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T11:24:56.000Z","msg":"安徽男子見女友落水竟逃跑了，致其溺亡！原因竟是&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n青春安徽&nbsp;2017-04-11<br />\n<br />\n2017年4月8號清晨，在安徽省安慶市懷寧縣高河鎮獨秀公園湖面上發現漂浮著一具屍體。公安和消防將女屍打撈上岸後，發現死者為年輕女性，下身赤裸。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/11/192320_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F11%2F192320_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=4f4b357c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今天，警方經過調查，公佈了案情經過，落水原因讓人唏噓不已！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/11/192341_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F11%2F192341_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=d72bb33b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/11/192407_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F11%2F192407_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=2e2d5c7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/11/192421_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F11%2F192421_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=a956637d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n懷寧縣公安局接到報警後，立即啟動命案偵破機制，市局刑警支隊派員進行現場指導，懷寧縣人民檢察院提前介入，經過一晝夜縝密偵查，查清案件基本事實。<br />\n<br />\n4月9日，王某某因未履行救助義務，涉嫌過失致人死亡被刑事拘留，案件還在進一步偵查中。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/11/192441_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F11%2F192441_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=d921759b&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}